articles.title: 2-Year-Old Girl First Case Of Human H5N1 Bird Flu Detected In Australia - IFLScience
articles.description: It’s believed she caught the infection while traveling in India.
articles.content: Australias first human case of H5N1 bird flu has been confirmed in a 2.5-year-old girl, who has now recovered after being treated in intensive care. The girl is thought to have contracted the virus i… [+2712 chars]
